      "role": "user",
      "content": "i literally cant even look at the news anymore without feeling like my heart is just sinking. everything is so doomed. like, what is even the point of planning a career or making friends or... anything? the world is just burning. it feels like we're all just watching a slow motion car crash and there's no way to stop it. it makes everything feel so pointless.",
